{"tid":1851390,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"搭飛機最慘遇到呢種人","createTime":"2020-01-30T04:23:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T07:30:49.000Z","uid":256585,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"396cd082a6063aa45c49ef03ca92bd2d6731c209","tid":1851390,"uid":256585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:23:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M37jXVt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM37jXVt.png&h=3588ca90&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kFEBZ8Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkFEBZ8Q.png&h=7219a1a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自己遲到仲要全世界等你一個<br />\n仲要搞到啲空姐開閘 仲好意思<br />\n行李都係要等下一班機 趕上機為乜呢<br />\n最撚戇鳩係要POST出嚟話俾人知<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n分享症<br />\n搭唔到就等下架啦<br />\n最撚乞人憎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdacca007f85b7fb3a7abf54faf81dcab4923999","tid":1851390,"uid":203619,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:24:27.000Z","msg":"總有呢啲傻閪既"},{"pid":"4cc254326397ce87dd2e8369ad7acbad878dd723","tid":1851390,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:24:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/308/5d9705d903228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F308%2F5d9705d903228.jpg&h=786cb045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">種族清洗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n透過邊境不設防<br />\n高調宣揚非本地人士免費優先治療武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蓄意引導大量染病支那人來港<br />\n摧毀香港已經長期超負荷的醫療系統，令香港人大規模感染<br />\n而無法隔離或治理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n中共打算將香港將變成武漢，市民無法睇醫生，橫屍街頭<br />\n意圖對香港人進行大屠殺</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n而家已經係獨立最佳時機，你，仲等緊啲咩<br />\n香港人，仲唔反佢老母？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：種族清洗 香港人，仲唔反佢老母<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1851323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1851323</a>"},{"pid":"c6c3e05c66d44b17cabd0c338a726218240d3551","tid":1851390,"uid":256585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdacca007f85b7fb3a7abf54faf81dcab4923999","tid":1851390,"uid":203619,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:24:27.000Z","msg":"總有呢啲傻閪既"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T04:26:38.000Z","msg":"仲要post 出嚟曬命係咩心態<br />\n<br />\n完全唔覺得羞恥"},{"pid":"9db0166ad866c286bb45242786250ca01b8af1e8","tid":1851390,"uid":178066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"r